MultiChannelConversionAttribution.ColumnConversionsDocumentation: 应用归因模型%s时此渠道的转化数.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.ColumnRevenueDocumentation: 应用归因模型%s时此渠道的收益.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.MultiAttributionEnabledForGoal: 为此目标启用了多渠道转化归因
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.Introduction: 启用此功能可以让您更准确地了解导致转化的不同来源。您将能够选择不同的归因模型，以查看哪些推荐人（或渠道）对转化的贡献最大，而不仅仅是将转化归因于上一次的非直接访问.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.ErrorMultiAttributionNotEnabled: 未为请求的目标启用多渠道归因
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.ErrorGoalDoesNotExist: 此网站不存在给定的目标
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.ErrorXNotWhitelisted: 不允许"%1$s"的值，请使用下列值之一：%2$s.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.NoGoalEnabled: 没有为此报表启用目标。至少具有写访问权限的用户可以在创建或编辑目标时启用属性报告.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.LastNonDirectInteractionDocumentation: 归因信用归最后一次非直接访问.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.LinearDocumentation: 归因信用在所有交互中平均分配.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.FirstInteractionDocumentation: 所有的归因积分只属于第一次互动.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.LastInteractionDocumentation: 所有的归因积分都只属于最后一次互动.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.PositionBasedDocumentation: Most of the attribution credit goes to the first and last interaction (40% each), the remaining credit is shared equally between all other interactions.
MultiChannelConversionAttribution.TimeDecayDocumentation: The attribution credit is shared across all interactions. The more recent an interaction was, the more credit it gets compared to an interaction that happened a longer time ago.
